channel.title: Vendor on The U2F Garden
channel.description: Recent content in Vendor on The U2F Garden

item.title: FeiTian
item.description: FeiTian (stylized as FEITIAN Technologies), established in 1998, is a Shenzhen based strong authentication and online security company. Their product line started with SmartCard and JavaCard products, later expanding into various mobile payment terminals in mainland China.

item.title: Google
item.description: Google’s Titan keys are a key part of their Advanced Protection program

item.title: GoTrustID
item.description: GoTrust provides FIPS-Compliant security keys in multiple forms, including traditional token and card forms.

item.title: HyperSecu
item.description: HyperSecu provides FIDO-certified tokens for individuals and enterprise.

item.title: Thetis
item.description: Thetis produces U2F and FIDO2 compliant tokens both with and without fingerprint biometrics.

item.title: TrustKey
item.description: TrustKey produces U2F tokens backed by a secure element designed by the parent company, eWBM.

item.title: Yubico
item.description: One of the leaders in security tokens, Yubico brought them to the masses through their Yubikey line.
